ivardefs.name: concept_
ivardefs.desc: Specifies a concept to be included or excluded.

ivardefs.name: filter_
ivardefs.desc: Select concepts by specify a matching criteria based on the properties (including relationships) defined by the system. If multiple filters are specified, they SHALL all be true.

ivardefs.name: system
ivardefs.desc: An absolute URI which is the code system from which the selected codes come from.

ivardefs.name: valueSet_
ivardefs.desc: Selects concepts found in this value set. This is an absolute URI that is a reference to ValueSet.url.

ivardefs.name: version
ivardefs.desc: The version of the code system that the codes are selected from.

properties.desc: Include one or more codes from a code system or other value set(s).
